ques et technologiques soulevés par l'intelligence artificielle, et tente de répondre à la question si complexe : les programmes pourront-ils être un jour réellement intelligents, créatifs, ou même conscients ?  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Apr 2022) 4aartificial intelligence. 4aneurosciences. 4aphilosophy. 7aCOMPUTERS / Intelligence (AI) & Semantics.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2z978311074335708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Engineering, Computer Sciences 2021z9783110753837oZDB-23-DEI08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEDP Sciences Frontlist eBook Package 2021z978311075665440uhttps://doi.org/10.1051/978-2-7598-2580-640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782759825806423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782759825806/original  a978-3-11-074335-7  DG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2b2021  a978-3-11-075665-4  EDP Sciences Frontlist eBook Package 2021b2021  aEBA_CL_CHCOMSGSEN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DEIb2021